                support, though commercial hosted versions are available from
                third parties like Mautic.com (by Acquia).
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                Can I use both platforms together?
              </h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Technically yes, but it's not recommended. You'd be managing
                separate contact databases, templates, and analytics across two
                systems. If you need Mautic's multi-channel features (SMS, push)
                alongside Notifuse's email capabilities, consider using Notifuse
                for email and dedicated tools for other channels instead.
              </p>
            </div>
